Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:45.60,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD7D7D7&\3c&H2A2A2A&\blur2\fscx50\pos(1190.075,15)}句
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:49.62,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}將悲傷與夢想與愛戀與手工小{\rED_CHS\blur2}垃圾{\r\blur2}收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:53.70,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秘密的寶箱 裝入心底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.74,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{你}　描繪的世界成為活下去的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.74,ED_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(696,23)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:02.66,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)\blur2}街上爽朗無風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:08.08,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}若是這首歌終有一天能{夠}　傳達到
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.91,0:23:08.08,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2\fscx60\pos(1094,15)}多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:08.08,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2\fscx50\pos(1110,15)}句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:12.52,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}僅是這樣必定能實現它的意義
