Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:39.72,ED_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(777,23)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:43.00,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即便講 世界天翻地覆
